spx.packets

Class AlertLogic

  • java.lang.Object
    • spx.packets.Alert
      • spx.packets.AlertLogic

  • public class AlertLogic
extends Alert
    AlertLogic

    The AlertLogic structure is used to report alerts that occur in response to SPx errors.

    This class is kept in sync with the C++ SPxPacketAlertLogic structure in "SPxPackets.h".

    See Also:
    Alert
